data.description: Clean and ready to renovate! Qualifies for 203K renovation loan. 3 large rooms to be reconfigured at your pleasure! Building was once an Army building and placed on lot as residence around 1941.Across the street from Zaragosa Park. Walk to ACC. One block off E. 7th St. Large trees.
